<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>9621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>17764</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>儿童中心夏令营的孩子们在外面吃午餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>17764</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>20523</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但是贾森没有吃。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>20523</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24175</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了，贾森？” 邓恩老师问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24175</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>26889</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你今天不饿吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>26889</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很饿。” 贾森指着西葫芦说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36109</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“但是我不想吃西葫芦了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36109</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41270</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我家菜园里有很多西葫芦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41270</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>44754</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我妈妈每天都让我吃！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>44754</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师很惊讶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>51499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“真的吗？你不想吃西葫芦了？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>51499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55481</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我很喜欢西葫芦。” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55481</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>59252</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不难吃啊。” 莉琪补充说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>59252</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62415</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就吃了吧，贾森。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62415</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68489</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“等等！” 邓恩老师突然用手盖住贾森的西葫芦。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68489</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71803</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都看着邓恩老师。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71803</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>74736</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么了？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>74736</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>78396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我刚想起来。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>78396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>83396</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们今天要做的东西可能会帮到你！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>83396</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>87321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师收好午餐。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>87321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要去拿些东西。” 他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90771</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>94291</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我可以帮忙吗？” 贾森问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>94291</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>103521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然了。你可以帮我拿东西。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>103521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>108536</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师在体育馆里拿起两个袋子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>108536</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>112711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他指了指桌上的插座和搅拌机。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>112711</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116540</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你可以帮我拿那些吗？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116540</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124263</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“可以。” 贾森把东西拿起来，跟着邓恩老师走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124263</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129509</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们要做一个神奇的蘸酱。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129509</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135841</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它可以让西葫芦，还有其它你不喜欢的蔬菜变得好吃。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>138265</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>伊坦皱了皱眉。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>138265</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>142573</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“包括花菜？” 他问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>142573</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>147244</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“当然包括花菜。” 邓恩老师回答说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>147244</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“神奇的蘸酱里有什么呢？” 伊坦问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，请给大家看看袋子里有什么。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156343</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163032</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师把袋子放在桌子上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163032</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165424</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“橄榄油和烤杏仁。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165424</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>170248</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森边说边从袋子里把东西拿出来，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>170248</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173060</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“柠檬和蒜。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173061</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>176869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就这些？” 伊坦惊讶地问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>176869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182579</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不。” 贾森说，“这里还有盐和胡椒。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182579</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>185588</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“男生们。” 邓恩老师说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>185588</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189607</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们可以挤出三汤匙的柠檬汁吗？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189607</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>201471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女生们，你们可以量出三分之一杯的橄榄油吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>201471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206887</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>邓恩老师给搅拌机插上电。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206887</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211877</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们可以把所有东西都放进去。” 他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>211877</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>220297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“烤杏仁、蒜、柠檬汁和橄榄油。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>220297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>225306</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>轰隆隆！搅拌机旋转着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>225306</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>231674</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在我们加入盐和胡椒。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>231674</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>235367</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“搅拌得很好了。” 莉琪说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>235367</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>240842</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“刚好可以做蘸酱。” 邓恩老师说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>240842</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>245362</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他拿了一点给贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>245362</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>249231</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“再试试西葫芦。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>249231</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257010</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大家都看着贾森。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257010</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>261869</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“怎么样？” 莉琪问，“喜欢吗？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>261869</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>264748</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>贾森慢慢吃着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>264748</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>267666</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“喜欢！” 他大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>267666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>273435</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“很好吃。试试吧！” 他对大家说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>273435</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>280235</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“成功了！” 波比说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>280235</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>285795</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“贾森，我们该叫它什么名字呢？” 邓恩老师问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>285795</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290150</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“儿童中心夏日蘸酱。” 贾森说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290150</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>300379</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我在家里也要做一次！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
